<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p style="font-size: 18px; color: #023761;"><strong>Buy one, get one half price Lift Pass Offer</strong></p>
<p>Book a ski holiday to <a data-udi="umb://document/a0f5a0d90fe3493faa137de4bb419db4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0f5a0d90fe3493faa137de4bb419db4}" title="Verbier">Verbier</a> <span>departing on 6 January and 7 April 2018</span> during W17/18 season and receive Buy One Get One Free Lift Passes. Book by 30th November 2017.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong>Terms and Conditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Applies to new bookings made from 13/07/2017 to 30/11/2017.</li>
<li><span>Applies to senior and adults passes only (groups, walker, cross-country, season, children and families passes excluded)</span>.</li>
<li><span>Must be added at the time of booking your ski holiday. Can be booked online, with our Reservations Team or through your Travel Agent</span>.</li>
<li><span>All prices, offers and availability are correct at time of publishing, are subject to change &amp; availability and can be withdrawn at any time</span>.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
